	en their detective skills by decoding secret messages\, solving riddles\, 
	and uncovering hidden clues to complete their top-secret missions. Nerf Ba
	ttles & Tactical Challenges – Gear up for friendly Nerf wars\, where teamw
	ork and strategy are key to outsmarting the opposition. Agents will also p
	ractice their precision and accuracy with target practice and stealth mane
	uvers. Escape Room-Style Puzzles – Secret agents will work together to cra
	ck codes\, unlock treasure chests\, and solve mind-bending puzzles before 
	time runs out! Outdoor Adventure & Camouflage Training – Spies will blend 
	into their surroundings\, practice silent movement\, and use nature to the
	ir advantage while completing their missions. This high-energy camp is per
	fect for kids who love adventure\, problem-solving\, and action-packed fun
